It was a really tough match last night. I started a bit slow. I was missing so many first serves and that cost me the set. I started coming back and playing much better in the second set and the last few games were almost perfect. I'm happy to finish like that. I got some rhythm at the end and some free points on my serve and that helped me a little bit. It has been fun on the court and this is good for my confidence. I hope I can have a couple more matches here.
